engal thanga raja ( tamil : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ராஜா ) is a 1973 indian tamil film , directed by v. b. rajendra prasad on his jagapathi art pictures banner and directed by v. b. rajendra prasad . starring sivaji ganesan , jayalalithaa , k. s. ravikumar and k. s. ravikumar in lead roles . the film had musical score by k. v. mahadevan .